# This is a yarn project (see apps/web package.json "packageManager" + CI
# `yarn install --frozen-lockfile`). yarn.lock is the single source of truth;
# ignore npm's package-lock.json so running `npm install` here can't recommit a
# competing lockfile that then drifts from yarn.lock.
